title: Beautiful Executive Condo-Mpls Skyline Views! Burnsville-Avail Sept1!
posting_body: ['Beautiful Executive Condo with Mpls Skyline Views!', 'Burnsville- Available Sept 1', 'Property Address', '12501 Nicollet Ave #410 | Burnsville, MN 55337', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'Homes For Now |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'Enjoy the open layout with Granite countertops, Maple cabinets, tiled & upgraded carpet floors, wide open floor plan with 9 foot ceilings.', 'Great Minneapolis skyline views from the deck!', 'Heated underground garage parking included!', 'Two Bedrooms including a Master Bedroom with Master Bath with separate shower and tub.', 'Third bedroom is non-conforming, perfect as a den/office with built in desk and storage shelves.', 'Laundry in-unit.', 'Internet, cable TV, water/sewer, trash, and exterior maintenance included in rent!', 'Unit also includes 2 parking spaces in the underground heated garage and a storage unit.', 'Building includes party room, exercise room and large outdoor patio area for grilling.', 'Within walking distance to Ames Center, restaurants, Cub foods and much more.', 'Tenant pays $200.00 HOA move in/out fee.', 'Pet Policy: One small pet allowed upon approval.', 'Available September 1, 2022.', 'MUST SEE!', 'More information on included internet & cable TV service through Xfinity:', 'Cable TV –  X1 Video service in HD including one DVR and one secondary box', 'Internet – Pro High Speed Internet 150Mbps includes the wireless modem', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 3BD/2.0BA', 'Square Feet: 1,382', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $2,395.00', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $2,395.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Small dogs allowed']
